33:58.900 --> 34:01.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHAD MARLOW, American Civil
Liberties Union: Schools need
to think about, how do we take

34:01.100 --> 34:04.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
on these issues in an
