fishing expeditions?

34:22.066 --> 34:25.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
CHAD MARLOW: No fishing
expeditions. And the
way to do that is by
not allowing passwords

34:25.100 --> 34:29.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
