47:23.100 --> 47:26.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID SEDARIS, Author, "Theft
By Finding": Trying this
persona on and that persona on

47:26.566 --> 47:31.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and, you know, trying acting,
