48:42.100 --> 48:45.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, you can't not
write and keep a diary?

48:45.200 --> 48:48.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID SEDARIS: Well, it's funny,
because, sometimes, people
would say, oh, that's very

48:48.933 --> 48:51.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
