I have to write about something

49:05.633 --> 49:09.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that ultimately doesn't matter
at all. But I -- I don't
know. I can't move on until I

49:10.466 --> 49:12.400 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
get that down.

49:12.400 --> 49:16.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: When you
overhear something or you record
something in your diary, is

49:16.033 --> 49:19.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
