JEFFREY BROWN:
Twenty-first draft?

51:49.466 --> 51:50.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID SEDARIS: Mm-hmm.

51:50.966 --> 51:54.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Is it tinkering
