52:03.966 --> 52:07.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And what does
a story in the end have to
have to be successful, to work

52:08.400 --> 52:10.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
for you?

52:10.533 --> 52:13.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DAVID SEDARIS: It used
to be about just racking
up laughs, right? But
I think you need, like,

52:16.133 --> 52:21.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
