a bit of weight. And that's
when you remember things.

52:23.600 --> 52:25.633 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
Or that's when I
remember things.

52:25.633 --> 52:30.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So people come
